data.title: Nana Ou-yang reaches all new level of fame after performance with Wiz Khalifa
data.meta_description: A lot has happened for Nana Ou-yang, but the most eventful, no doubt, was her performance with Wiz Khalifa.
data.text:
Ou-yang and Khalifa performed the latter's Grammy-nominated hit, See You Again. She may only be 17, but with two albums, six films and more than 1 million Instagram followers to her name, it's clear she is already something of a veteran.

A lot has happened to the artist since we spoke to her in 2016; no doubt 2018 will see her adding even more amazing achievements to her CV.
